name: Astros Boy
description:
I wouldn't say I like sports that much; They bored me a bit; I went to an Astros game on Tuesday, it was more fun than I was expecting and of course, my camera always makes everything better. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The Houston Astros are an American professional baseball team based in Houston.
